product_name: Green Trails North Skyline Mid-Peninsula Map
long_description: The Green Trails North Skyline Mid-Peninsula map offers a beautifully detailed topographic guide to the coastal south side of California's Bay Area. Printed on waterproof and tear-resistant paper, this map stands up to the rigors of your outdoor adventure. Main map features a scale of 1:50,000; inset maps feature a scale of 1:35,000. The Green Trails North Skyline Mid-Peninsula map measures 24 x 18 in. (9 x 6 in. folded). Green Trails Maps; copyright 2012.
